  <h2><a href="../../blog-posts/president-hu-and-president-obama-washington-advancing-clean-energy-partnership-between-un" title="President Hu and President Obama in Washington: Advancing the clean energy partnership between the United States and China">President Hu and President Obama in Washington: Advancing the clean energy partnership between the United States and China</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by Barbara Finamore on Jan 25, 2011</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
